===Etymology===
From {{LL.}} {{term|idioma}} < {{etyl|grc}} {{term|ιδίωμα|sc=polytonic|tr=idioma||a peculiarity, property, a peculiar phraseology, idiom}} < {{term|ιδιοῦσθαι|tr=idiousthai||to make one's own, appropriate to oneself}} < {{term|ἴδιος||one's own, pertaining to oneself, private, personal, peculiar, separate|tr=idios|lang=grc|sc=polytonic}}.

